1 Aham adṛkṣam aśvavāhinam sainyam calantam,
2 ākramaṇam ārabhamāṇam ātmīyam pradarśanam ca kurvāṇam,
3 kadācit svasthānārthaṃ viṣamam āpannam ca;

4 Aham adṛkṣam dhāvantam sainyam tava bhūmau,
5 he Aretinaḥ, adṛkṣam ca gavalanaṃ gacchan,
6 yuddhaṃ kurvatāṃ āhatya ca yuddhaṃ kridantaṃ ca;

7 kadācit śaṅkhaih, kadācit ghanṭāih,
8 bherībhīḥ ca durgāṇāṃ saṃjñābhiś ca,
9 svakīyābhiś ca parakīyābhiś ca vastubhiḥ;

28 Tathā sarvataḥ pāpinaḥ sthitāḥ āsīt;
29 Yada tu Barbaricciḥ samīpe ājagāma,
30 Tathā uṣṇajale nimajjitāḥ abhavan.

31 Aham apaśyam, athavā mama hṛdayam adhunāpi tatas tiryag bhavati,
32 Ekam tatra sthitam āsannam iva, yathā sa milati
33 Ekena mandukena sthitena, anyena mandukena kṣipram gacchatā;

46 Mama naiḥkaḥ tasya sānnidhyam ājagāma;
47 tasya pṛcchati sma kutaḥ asi, sa ca pratyāha:
48 "Aham Nāvarra rājyāt sambhūtaḥ.

52 Tataḥ aham asmi kulam śreṣṭhasya rājñaḥ Thibault;
53 tatra aham āsītām vyāpāram kartum,
54 yasya hetum aham adyāpi dāhaṃ bhajāmi.

58 Duritapiśācikānāṃ madhye mūṣiko jātaḥ āsīt;
59 Api tu Barbaricciyā saḥ bāhūnābhyām gṛhītaḥ āsīt
60 Evaṃ ca uktam āsīt: "Yāvat aham enam bandhāmi tāvat tvam tatra tiṣṭha."

61 Sa ca mama gurum prati mukham cakāra;
62 "Pṛcchasi," āha, "punar api, yadi tvam icchasi
63 adhikam jñātum tasmāt, pūrvam anyaḥ enam vināśayet."

91 Oho, paśyata anyamapi yaḥ daśanān praghṛṣati;
92 Aham api vakṣyāmi, kim tu bibhemi yaḥ
93 Mama śirojuṣṭikāṃ kharḍīkartum udyataḥ asti.

97 "Yadi paśyataḥ śrotum vā icchathas",
98 punar ārabhata bhayakṛtaḥ paścāt,
99 "Tuṣkān vā Lombārdān vā, aham ānayāmi;

100 api tu Malebranche alpaṃ kālaṃ viśrāntim āgacchantu,
101 yathā te na bibhyuḥ teṣāṃ pratiśodhanāt;
102 aham ca, asmin eva sthāne upaviśya,

121 Navarasaḥ svayam samayaṃ gṛhītavān;
122 sthāpayāmāsa pādāv adhaḥ, tataś ca ekasmin kṣaṇe
123 alampata, tataś ca teṣāṃ prayojane tataḥ vimuktaḥ abhavat.

133 Calcabrinaḥ krodhād buffāyāḥ,
134 patantam anugacchan pakṣaiḥ, abhilāṣī
135 yasya jīvanam yuddhasya prāptau;

142 Uṣṇo ghaṭakastatraiva muktaḥ āsīt;
143 Api tu uttiṣṭhitum na śakyate sma,
144 Tathā tasya pakṣau saṃliptāvabhūtām.

148 Iha, amutra avajagmuḥ sthānam;
149 ankān daduḥ śūlaiḥ ākrāntānām,
150 ye ca āsanta abhyantara-paripācitāḥ.
